# <span style="color:#FF2079">PARENTS!</span>

We would like your children to be included in these emails.  In
order for your children to receive these emails, <span
style="color:#FF2079;font-size:larger">**YOU**</span>, their
parents, must enter their email addresses into
[churchofjesuschrist.org](https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/?lang=eng&_r=1).
(To be clear, youth leaders cannot do this for you.)

## Instructions

1. Go to [churchofjesuschrist.org](https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/?lang=eng&_r=1)
2. Click on "My Account and Ward".
3. Sign into your account.
4. Click on "Ward Directory and Map".
5. Find your child's name.
6. Click on the edit pencil and enter their email address.

## Problems?

If the above instructions aren't working for you, please contact
[Sister Nelson](mailto:sully1234@gmail.com) for more help.

